description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'HIIT Row' from the channel Mike Dostal.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The The Firestarter vibe means Fast, explosive, and electrifying. Short but devastating. This is especially good for When you only have 10-20 minutes but want to give 1000%. The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible..
The technique difficulty is Advanced.
The effort required is Challenging and Extreme.

Original workout description: Give it all you've got for 15 strokes at the top of every minute with Mike. 

Max rhythm: 32, Format: HIIT...
